Sunjammer's TileMagic System - Autotile

Can be placed either at design time by a builder or during a game by a DM.  Once placed this will convert itself into a TileMagic tile or tiles (according to its setting).  There is a 6 second delay (1 heartbeat) before it activates.  It is destoyed in the process.

Must be tagged sj_tilemagic_autotile and have sj_tilemagic_hb script to function correctly.
